{"tid":1219834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於呢幾日發生既事 我有少少野想講","createTime":"2019-06-14T01:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T09:48:36.000Z","uid":88117,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1dfc132a29fc14aa2bb23c61205a0e07280ad4f","tid":1219834,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IjqVrd6wshE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIjqVrd6wshE&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=cf316b44\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IjqVrd6wshE</a><br />\n<br />\n係抗爭階段每個人都有自己嘅職責<br />\n現時身處異地有玩開rap嘅我<br />\n唯一可以做嘅就係寫歌<br />\n去令更多人去知道依件事情嘅嚴重性<br />\n喚醒更多人去關注<br />\n我冇得唔去做 因為係我內心促使我去行動<br />\n更何況hip hop 其中一個好大嘅存在價值就係為群眾發聲<br />\n去表達自己嘅諗法 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港加油</span>"},{"pid":"80687ac009011f4eb56b1d8f4b7d13103bea207b","tid":1219834,"uid":143166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhh"},{"pid":"dfe561510bef0eb7d45a0f6f655f6334de93f5b1","tid":1219834,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c6a6a7df701d299be19b1f40c140e3bfca342b","tid":1219834,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819f1d88cf979238e9ac37cecdb35a83e9f8e2dd","tid":1219834,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"5215b5cd38897249faab8cb8a3978a68c87acdec","tid":1219834,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:56:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5c6168168d3d304b7fbefdb1baea089734bf3cb","tid":1219834,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:14:45.000Z","